snippet.title: Diner Out | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Merge matching kitchen ingredients to cook delicious dishes and keep hungry customers happy in this cozy game. Turn your café into the talk of the town!

Play Diner Out on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81675949

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
